headline: SCHW to Feel the Heat as Vanguard Greenlights Crypto-Product Trading?
summary: Vanguard's crypto shift trims Schwab's edge, but rising ETF activity may still play to SCHW's platform strengths.

headline: Barclays has a Positive Outlook on The Charles Schwab Corporation (SCHW)
summary: The Charles Schwab Corporation (NYSE:SCHW) is one of the best dividend stocks in the financial sector. On November 7, Barclays analyst Benjamin Budish assigned a Buy rating on Charles Schwab, setting $115 as the price target. In a separate business update, SCHW disclosed on November 14 that it has authorized senior notes worth $2 billion. […]
